		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2">Tank class balancing<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Tank class balancing";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted: Sat, Sep 10th 11:30 AM 2005 EST</span><span class="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=1;mid=1126366483280704902;num=10;page=1;post=1;replyto=1126366483280704902"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a>    <a name="1126366483280704902"></a></span></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" class="mform" ><span class="fs8"><span class="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=538892"><span class="">hkain</span></a><b><span class=""></span></b><br />3 posts
		   <br /><span class="nobr"><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Decent  </span><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist;addname=hkain;type=Address" class="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book" /> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1" alt=""/></span></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%">
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;I think sony could do one thing to make us warriors = the knight classes.  Alow us to use the pal/sk one handers that are available, provided we use a shield with them.  Contrary to what alot of people believe we don't do more melee dps than the night classes do with one handers and shields. Take the Shiny Hammer of Caos for instance 40/28 with ac 10. That weapon is better dps for a knight class than any byeable two hander we warriors can use.  Not to mention that bash with high ac shield equiped can do alot of damage.  I sometimes crit for 500 on a bash with a 45 ac shield.  This would also allow us to take advantage of the shield block aa alot more than we can now.  I have parsed alot of my fights and I find that when at haste cap I do more dps useing an edge of envelopment 44/34 than I do useing one handers, even 18/20 and 17/19 one handers.  Granted when not at haste cap it seems I do more damage with one handers.  If we could do the same dps with one handers that we do now or better even, then add the bash damage to it, I think we would be alot more sought after for groups.  I know many will say its not our job to do damage its to take damage.  I agree but this would not only help our dps it would allso allow us to take less damage.  More ac not to mention shield block and bash stun.  I just can't understand why this hasn't been implimented long before now.  It wouldn't take anything away from the knight classes they will still be wanted in groups for there spell abilitys.  I would like to hear your thoughts on this. <br /> <br /> <br />Thats my 2cp! <br /> <br />Lete 69 Ogre Warrior Prexus</p>
