		   <br /><span class="nobr"><span class="notbold">Score</span>: Decent  </span><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist;addname=Tawynia;type=Address" class="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book" /> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1" alt=""/></span></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%">
<p>I would personally perfer that they gave us a stun disc. with a reasonable reset time and cost. they could even make it a higher end disc. as it stands we don't get a disc for level 67. But thats just me, I don't even want it for agro, I just hate gating mobs and would like to have a reasonable interupt, instead of hoping for a proc. <br /> <br />ps of course the added hate would be nice too. =P <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sat Sep 10 19:02:26 2005 by Tawynia</span></i></p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td class="fs8"></td></tr></table>
